name: LOST
description:
"LOST" / METACHROMATIC SERIES (2/3)
Graphite Pencil on Paper
2550x3500
300dpi
Personal Use Only

- I lost myself trying to please everyone. Now I am losing everyone as I find myself. -

This work is visualization of a person who is get lost and trapped in endless anxiety, emotionally crisis and fear to get out of these emotions. But on the other hand, the person have to be able to do good values for everyone around.
